members.description: Error code rejected from upload with FileTransferErrorDefined in FileTransferError.     FILE_NOT_FOUND_ERR: 1   Return when file was not found     INVALID_URL_ERR: 2,     Return when url was invalid     CONNECTION_ERR: 3,      Return on connection error     ABORT_ERR: 4,           Return on aborting     NOT_MODIFIED_ERR: 5     Return on '304 Not Modified' HTTP response
